ived as a continuous\nmaterial medium, still stands up as a physical reality and could be physically\nassociated with dark matter, the cosmic background radiation and the vacuum\ncondensates of particle physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2010 20:59:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Apr 2010 18:53:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Dec 2010 23:17:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-12-17"}
