ric exponential scaling of unitary decompositions\ncombined with the highly recursive structure of our scheme required to overcome\nthe no-signalling constraint of relativistic causality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Apr 2010 14:55:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2010 14:46:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
